    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for exceptional high-revving response. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise shift gates, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal power distribution across the rear axle. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and a comprehensive subframe inspection. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals remain strong, offering a visceral driving experience with pure analog feedback. Ideal for the driver who values mechanical integrity and the characteristic rasp of an atmospheric M-car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
