    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and comfort. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only minor road wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of any significant blemishes, while all electronic features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is sound, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and scheduled maintenance intervals. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. It sits on a set of high-tread tires mounted on clean alloy wheels. If you are looking for a reliable, honest car that has been treated with respect and is ready for the road today, this is the perfect choice.",
      "price": 36500.0,
